 & = & \boldsymbol{\xi}\left(\mathbf{x}^{\prime}\right)\cdot\left(\hat{\mathbf{x}}\xi_{x}\left(-\frac{1}{s}+\frac{s_{x}^{2}}{s^{3}}\right)+\hat{\mathbf{y}}\xi_{y}\left(-\frac{1}{s}+\frac{s_{y}^{2}}{s^{3}}\right)+\hat{\mathbf{z}}\xi_{z}\left(-\frac{1}{s}+\frac{s_{z}^{2}}{s^{3}}\right)\right)\\
