)
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\boldsymbol{\xi}\left(\mathbf{r}\right)=\mu_{01}\delta^{3}\left(\left|\mathbf{r}^{\prime}+\mathbf{s}\right|\right)\hat{\mathbf{z}}\approx\mu_{01}\delta^{3}\left(\left|\mathbf{s}\right|\right)\hat{\mathbf{z}}=\mu_{01}\delta^{3}\left(s\right)\hat{\mathbf{z}}
